{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":105,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lao_ai","speaker_name":"嫪毐","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"吕不韦实在欺人太甚。","tone":"沉声","chapter":214,"line_start":12,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lao_ai","text":"目前形势下，内史大人还是忍一时之气吧！犯不着为一个女人与他正面冲突。","tone":"无奈","chapter":214,"line_start":16,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_lao_ai","speaker_name":"嫪毐","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项兄看到美美的无奈和痛苦吗？她的心是向着我的。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":214,"line_start":20,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_lao_ai","speaker_name":"嫪毐","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我要杀了吕不韦！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":214,"line_start":26,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lao_ai","text":"先不说能否杀死他，但若吕不韦真的死了，秦国会立即陷进乱局里，嫪兄还是三思才好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":214,"line_start":28,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_lao_ai","speaker_name":"嫪毐","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项兄明天是否打算杀死邱日升？","tone":"疑问","chapter":214,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lao_ai","text":"这事由嫪兄作主好了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":214,"line_start":44,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_lao_ai","speaker_name":"嫪毐","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项兄很够朋友，这事情我是明白的。邱日升实在太过分，但此人目前对我仍有点用处，项兄给他一些挫折便罢！","tone":"激动","chapter":214,"line_start":48,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lao_ai","text":"就依嫪兄之言好了。","tone":"淡然","chapter":214,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_lao_ai","text":"嫪兄和蒲鶮究竟是怎么样的关系？","tone":"疑问","chapter":214,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_lao_ai","speaker_name":"嫪毐","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"现在他致力巴结我，我见没有什么害处，便敷衍一下他。此人在秦、赵均有庞大的势力，以前一直和阳泉君勾结，现在失去靠山，又见杜璧没有什么作为，自然要另外找人支撑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":214,"line_start":58,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_wu_guo","speaker_name":"乌果"