{"segment":2,"line_start":106,"line_end":215,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"明天三弟真的要为嫪毐而放弃铲除邱日升的良机吗？","tone":"沉声","chapter":214,"line_start":108,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"想深一层，现在仍不宜除去邱日升，多个人与吕不韦作对该是好事。","tone":"无奈","chapter":214,"line_start":112,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"有嫣然主持，夫君大人放心好了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":214,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":null,"text":"大家早点休息，养足精神，明天便到那破行馆大闹一场，使人知道我们绝不好惹。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":214,"line_start":120,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_zhao_zhi","speaker_name":"赵致","listener":null,"text":"现在我们的项爷惯了在开战前到醉风楼逛逛，不过今次恐怕没有人敢再下重注买项爷输了。","tone":"调侃","chapter":214,"line_start":124,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"理财之道，在于应加则加，应减得减，用得其所。今我大秦国库充盈，积粟如山，民以殷盛，国以富强，百姓乐用，诸侯亲服，自应多开财路，广增赋税，奋勇东进。只有多占土地，我大秦方可继续强国强兵的策略，此实我大秦开国以来，前所未有统一天下的良机。","tone":"得意","chapter":214,"line_start":142,"line_end":148},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_chang_ping_jun","text":"左相有何意见？","tone":"疑问","chapter":214,"line_start":160,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_chang_ping_jun","speaker_name":"昌平君","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"我大秦自孝公败楚、魏之师，举地千里；惠文王拔三川之地，西并巴、蜀，北牧上郡，南取汉中，包九夷，制鄢、郢。昭襄王强公室，杜私斗，蚕食六国之从，使之西面事秦。至今更新得东三郡，诚宜先行富民之策，巩固所得之地。兼之现在郑国渠筑建在在需财，大批农民因被征作渠工，致荒废生产，故增赋之议，还请储君三思。","tone":"严肃","chapter":214,"line_start":164,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_wang_wan","speaker_name":"王绾","listener":"char_chang_ping_jun","text":"左相此言差矣，我大秦乃天府之国，进可攻，退可守，关中左殽函，右陇蜀，沃野千里，南有巴蜀之饶，北有胡苑之利，阻三面而固守，独以一面东制诸侯，兵源粮草补充无缺，建郑国渠只是九牛一毛，只巴、蜀两郡已足可应付。请储君明鉴。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":214,"line_start":174,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_meng_ao","speaker_name":"蒙骜","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"我大秦自昭襄王以还，奋力东进，不仅取得赵、魏、韩、楚的大片土地，且大小战数百次，歼敌将士百万以上，大大削弱东方诸国的战斗力量。眼下东方六国民不聊生，族类离散，乱极思治，际此众弱而我独强之时，我大秦占尽天时、地利、人和之势，若不趁机举财扩军，错失良机，岂对得起诸先王乎？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":214,"line_start":178,"line_end":182},{"speaker":"char_chang_ping_jun","speaker_name":"昌平君","listener":null,"text":"有请李斯大人把研究所得，奏禀储君。","tone":"陈述","chapter":214,"line_start":194,"line_end":196},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"统一天下，乃我大秦国策，此事当无人心怀异议。惟施政有若怒海操舟，稍一不慎，重则舟覆人亡，轻亦民变祸连，故绝不可操之过急，其要在体察民情，因情施政。","tone":"严肃","chapter":214,"line_start":206,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_cai_ze","speaker_name":"蔡泽","listener":"char_li_si","text":"老臣等在仲父指示下，遍察我大秦各郡，因地制宜，厘定赋税，绝不会轻忽从事，长史大人实在过虑了。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":214,"line_start":212,"line_end":214}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiao_pan","name":"小盘","alias":["嬴政","储君"],"identity":"秦国储君","faction":"秦廷系","role":"protagonist","archetype":"scholar","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"秦国未来的秦始皇，年少有为，深谋远虑","personality":{"traits":["聪慧过人","沉着冷静","有帝王之相","善于隐忍","果断"],"speech_style":"威严","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"挚友","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"信赖"},{"target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"宿敌","intensity":70,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"对抗"},{"target":"char_li_si","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"信任"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[214],"source_refs":[{"chapter":214,"line_start":132,"line_end":132,"text":"一个月前向小盘提交洋洋万言的预算案"}]},{"id":"char_li_si","name":"李斯","alias":["长史大人"],"identity":"秦国长史","faction":"秦廷系","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"秦国重臣，才华横溢的政治家，名垂千古","personality":{"traits":["才华横溢","善于辩论","高瞻远瞩","沉着冷静","深谋远虑"],"speech_style":"从容不迫","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"效忠"},{"target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"宿敌","intensity":70,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"对抗"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[214],"source_refs":[{"chapter":214,"line_start":206,"line_end":206,"text":"李斯心中暗喜，欣然走出来"}]},{"id":"char_chang_ping_jun","name":"昌平君","alias":["左相"],"identity":"秦国左相","faction":"秦廷系","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"秦国左相，忠于秦王的政治盟友","personality":{"traits":["忠诚","有智谋","善于进言","正直","有担当"],"speech_style":"庄重","temperament":"正直"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":75,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"效忠"},{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"盟友"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[214],"source_refs":[{"chapter":214,"line_start":164,"line_end":164,"text":"昌平君振起精神"}]},{"id":"char_wang_ling","name":"王陵","alias":[],"identity":"秦国将领","faction":"秦廷系","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"秦国武将，忠于秦王","personality":{"traits":["忠勇","武艺高强","耿直","不善言辞"],"speech_style":"直率","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"效忠"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[214],"source_refs":[{"chapter":214,"line_start":136,"line_end":136,"text":"小盘、李斯、昌平君和王陵不时密议"}]},{"id":"char_wang_wan","name":"王绾","alias":[],"identity":"秦国大臣","faction":"吕不韦派","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"吕不韦一党的大臣，善于辞令","personality":{"traits":["善于辩论","趋炎附势","圆滑","有才学"],"speech_style":"犀利","temperament":"圆滑"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"主仆","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"依附"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[214],"source_refs":[{"chapter":214,"line_start":174,"line_end":174,"text":"王绾冷笑一声"}]},{"id":"char_cai_ze","name":"蔡泽","alias":[],"identity":"秦国老臣","faction":"吕不韦派","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"吕不韦一党的老臣，轻视李斯","personality":{"traits":["傲慢","趋炎附势","保守","自以为是"],"speech_style":"不屑","temperament":"傲慢"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_bu_wei","type":"主仆","intensity":55,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"依附"},{"target":"char_li_si","type":"对手","intensity":40,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"轻视"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[214],"source_refs":[{"chapter":214,"line_start":212,"line_end":212,"text":"蔡泽显然一点都看不起李斯"}]},{"id":"char_meng_ao","name":"蒙骜","alias":[],"identity":"秦国老将","faction":"秦廷系","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"秦国的老将军，经验丰富，支持东进策略","personality":{"traits":["老当益壮","经验丰富","好战","忠诚","豪迈"],"speech_style":"豪迈激昂","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":65,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"效忠"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[214],"source_refs":[{"chapter":214,"line_start":178,"line_end":178,"text":"蒙骜接着道"}]},{"id":"char_wang_he","name":"王龁","alias":[],"identity":"秦国将领","faction":"秦廷系","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"秦国武将，不善政治辩论","personality":{"traits":["忠勇","武艺高强","耿直","不善言辞"],"speech_style":"直率","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":55,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"效忠"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[214],"source_refs":[{"chapter":214,"line_start":202,"line_end":202,"text":"王龁、王陵等属武将"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":216,"line_end":314,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_li_si","text":"长史大人若有机会亲体政情，方能明白本仲父今次呈上储君的建议书，实是穷无数人力物力而得来千锤百炼的成果，我大秦之兴，尽在其中矣。请储君、太后赐准，好立即实施。","tone":"得意","chapter":214,"line_start":216,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"所谓体察民情，必须有实据支持，始能令人信服。若照仲父提议，诸郡之中，以巴、蜀两郡增税最苛，此便是万万不行。","tone":"淡然","chapter":214,"line_start":222,"line_end":226},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_li_si","text":"富者增之，贫者减之，此乃赋税之金科玉律，巴蜀乃天府之地，我大秦资其富，用兼天下。长史何有此言？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":214,"line_start":228,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"巴蜀不但是我大秦根本，还是战略重地，其地兵甲，若由岷江顺流而下，五天可达楚郢，乃统一西南和伐楚的必争之地，为可巩固巴蜀，必须因情施政，改采优宠之策。但微臣却在仲父的建议书看不到此点。","tone":"严肃","chapter":214,"line_start":232,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"要知巴蜀虽资源丰富，却是地广人稀，民智较低，很多地方还是处于刀耕火种的原始阶段，若骤增其赋，恐怕一旦超过其负担能力，反因加得减。其次巴蜀土著种族众多，强悍善战，若激起民变，纵能平定，亦必大伤元气，加深仇隙。故不若减轻赋租，使人心归向，始是上策。微臣之议，立足点在于巴蜀的战略性更胜于其经济上的考虑，请储君、太后和仲父明察。","tone":"严肃","chapter":214,"line_start":236,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"李卿所言有理，先还富于民，然后再取富于民，始是正略。争天下岂在乎一年、两年之短长，何况左相言及郑国渠耗费一事，绝非九牛一毛，若抽空巴、蜀两地资源，势必激起民变，那寡人就真的愧对先王了。","tone":"激动","chapter":214,"line_start":244,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"现今初得东三郡，只是减税，仍未足以安民，微臣之议，最好减轻刑罚。我大秦眼下不是患无刑，而是患刑重。盗一钱者重罚，知情不报者罪同，轻罪重罚，刑何以苛，对巴、蜀等蛮夷众多又或新郡新民之地，刑苛只会酿成民变，于我大秦一统天下大大不利。","tone":"严肃","chapter":214,"line_start":254,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"富国之策，千变万化，但万变不离其宗，用之所得是也。像巴蜀之地，地广人稀，人才缺乏，但如能徙富民于巴蜀，刺激工商，资我本土，两地振兴有望。我大秦始能得其利，足用之以并天下。","tone":"陈述","chapter":214,"line_start":262,"line_end":266},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"李卿之言对极，众卿还有何话可说？","tone":"欣喜","chapter":214,"line_start":268,"line_end":270},{"speaker":"char_lao_ai","speaker_name":"嫪毐","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"李大人之贤，可比商鞅而尤有过之。微臣斗胆请储君破格赐准李卿，依仲父之议，重新厘定赋财之策，请储君明鉴。","tone":"认真","chapter":214,"line_start":272,"line_end":276},{"speaker":"char_zhu_ji","speaker_name":"朱姬","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"王儿看着办好了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":214,"line_start":290,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_li_si","text":"李卿立即着手进行此事，完成后需一式两份，分别呈上寡人和仲父，待寡人和仲父商量后，再在廷上商讨。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":214,"line_start":294,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"长史大人果然不负本仲父所望，为我大秦立下大功，理该奖赏，不若就到本仲父处来负责赋役之务，使长史得以尽展抱负。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":214,"line_start":302,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_lv_bu_wei","text":"仲父所言甚是，不过寡人心中早有更适合李卿的职位，春祭时会有公告。","tone":"微笑","chapter":214,"line_start":306,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"今天到此为止，其他事留待明天禀上，退朝！","tone":"严肃","chapter":214,"line_start":310,"line_end":310}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
